      },
      "date": "2015-03-19 15:21:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> I wonder why I haven't seen that failure before. I ran that test many time and it went though maloo a few times too. So why now?\n\nPerhaps higher memory pressure on the autotest nodes (the VMs only have 2GB) makes it more likely that the object has been purged from the cache before we call fid2path.",
